Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:33.05,02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an9}歌：西木野真姫(CV.Pile)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:39.09,02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\fs50}I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.73,02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\fs50}Hey,hey,hey,START:DASH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:49.05,02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\fs50}Hey,hey,hey,START:DASH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:55.90,02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\fs50}その日が絶対來る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:55.90,02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\fs50}那一天一定会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.85,02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\fs50}君も感じてるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.85,02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\fs50}你也能感觉得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:02.89,02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\fs50}始まりの鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:02.89,02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\fs50}启程时心中的鼓动
